snippet.title: Amber Heard Accuses Johnny Depp of Trying To Stir Sh....
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Accuses Johnny Depp of Trying To Stir Sh....

The 35-year-old actress was granted a motion to dismiss the 57-year-old actor's defamation case against her for the third time by a Virginia judge. However, it was then reported that if she is found to have committed perjury during the court case, she would face legal repercussions in the form of sanctions or fines.
